OL,6,FMore than 30 firefighters have been
OL,7,Ftackling a huge blaze which broke out
OL,8,Finside a former school building .
OL,10,FSeven fire crews were called out to
OL,11,Fthe old school premises in Clifton
OL,12,FRoad, in , yesterday afternoon.
OL,14,FClifton Road and Hertford Road were
OL,15,Fclosed while firefighters worked at
OL,16,Fthe scene.
OL,18,FBrunswick Road, between White Road and
OL,19,FHertford Road was also closed. Police
OL,20,Fofficers were assisting with traffic
OL,21,Fmanagement.
