OL,6,FShe said staff and pupils had moved to
OL,7,Fa different site nearby.JThe acting co-
OL,8,Fheadteacher wrote on social media
OL,9,Fplatform X: "We are so sad to see our
OL,10,Fold Clifton building on fire. There
OL,11,Fare many of us who have happy memories
OL,12,Fof teaching here or being a pupil.J"I
OL,13,Fstarted teaching here in 1997 and Mrs
OL,14,FHemming in 1995. We have lots of staff
OL,15,Fchildren and parents who have
OL,16,Fmemories.J"We are still Clifton
OL,17,FPrimary School, we just moved into a
OL,18,Fbuilding round the corner. The old
OL,19,Fbuilding has a special place in all
OL,20,Four hearts."
