OL,6,FFormer pupil Kamran Shezad said he was
OL,7,Fheartbroken after seeing the damage
OL,8,Fcaused by the fire.
OL,10,FHe said: "This is heartbreaking. My
OL,11,Flocal primary school from 1987-91.
OL,12,F"Many wonderful memories of friends,
OL,13,Fteachers and the iconic building
OL,14,Fitself. The old Clifton School
OL,15,Fbuilding has been in my sight my
OL,16,Fentire life, so this is devastating to
OL,17,Fsee."JAnother former pupil who later
OL,18,Fwent on to the teach at the school
OL,19,Fsaid online they were "saddened" by
OL,20,Fthe blaze.
